name: Proto Tower 9
description: This is part of a dual set, 9 and 10. trying to see how long it takes to do two. i also find myself wanting to come up with new background patterns every time even though it would probably be better if i standardized the names, or limited myself from time to time to a certain set, to keep the traits reined in a bit... wreigned in... rein in? is that how it's spelled? writing on a text editor doesn't afford the same sort of spell check as writing in a word processor. who cares though right?
